1096    def Overview(self, showStatistics: bool = False) -> dict:
1097        """
1098        Get portfolio: all open positions, orders and some statistics for defined accountId.
1099        If `overviewFile` is define then also save information to file.
1100
1101        :param showStatistics: if `False` then only dictionary returns, if `True` then show more debug information.
1102        :return: dictionary with client's raw portfolio and some statistics.
1103        """
1104        view = {
1105            "raw": {  # --- raw portfolio responses from broker with user portfolio data:
1106                "headers": {},  # list of dictionaries, response headers without "positions" section
1107                "Currencies": [],  # list of dictionaries, open trades with currencies from "positions" section
1108                "Shares": [],  # list of dictionaries, open trades with stocks from "positions" section
1109                "Bonds": [],  # list of dictionaries, open trades with bonds from "positions" section
1110                "Etfs": [],  # list of dictionaries, open trades with etfs from "positions" section
1111                "Futures": [],  # list of dictionaries, open trades with futures from "positions" section
1112                "positions": {},  # raw response from broker: dictionary with current available or blocked currencies and instruments for client
1113                "orders": [],  # raw response from broker: list of dictionaries with all pending (market) orders
1114                "stopOrders": [],  # raw response from broker: list of dictionaries with all stop orders
1115                "currenciesCurrentPrices": {"rub": {"name": "Российский рубль", "currentPrice": 1.}},  # dict with prices of all currencies in RUB
1116            },
1117            "stat": {  # --- some statistics calculated using "raw" sections:
1118                "portfolioCostRUB": 0.,  # portfolio cost in RUB (Russian Rouble)
1119                "currentBlockedRUB": 0.,  # blocked sum in Russian Rouble
1120                "totalChangesRUB": 0.,  # changes for all open trades in RUB
1121                "totalChangesPercentRUB": 0.,  # changes for all open trades in percents
1122                "allCurrenciesCostRUB": 0.,  # costs of all currencies (include rubles) in RUB
1123                "availableRUB": 0.,  # available rubles (without other currencies)
1124                "stocksCostRUB": 0.,  # costs of all stocks in RUB
1125                "bondsCostRUB": 0.,  # costs of all bonds in RUB
1126                "etfsCostRUB": 0.,  # costs of all etfs in RUB
1127                "Currencies": [],  # list of dictionaries of all currencies statistics
1128                "Shares": [],  # list of dictionaries of all stocks statistics
1129                "Bonds": [],  # list of dictionaries of all bonds statistics
1130                "Etfs": [], # list of dictionaries of all etfs statistics
1131                "Futures": [], # list of dictionaries of all futures statistics
1132                "orders": [],  # list of dictionaries of all pending (market) orders and it's parameters
1133                "stopOrders": [],  # list of dictionaries of all stop orders and it's parameters
1134                "blockedCurrencies": {},  # dict with blocked instruments and currencies, e.g. {"rub": 1291.87, "usd": 6.21}
1135                "blockedInstruments": {},  # dict with blocked  by FIGI, e.g. {}
1136            },
1137            "analytics":{  # --- some analytics of portfolio:
1138                "distrByAssets": {},  # portfolio distribution by assets
1139                "distrByCompanies": {},  # portfolio distribution by companies
1140                "distrBySectors": {},  # portfolio distribution by sectors
1141                "distrByCurrencies": {},  # portfolio distribution by currencies
1142            }
1143        }
1144
1145        if showStatistics:
1146            uLogger.debug("Request portfolio of a client...")
1147
1148        portfolioResponse = self.RequestPortfolio()  # current user's portfolio (dict)
1149        view["raw"]["positions"] = self.RequestPositions()  # current open positions by instruments (dict)
1150        view["raw"]["orders"] = self.RequestPendingOrders()  # current actual pending orders (list)
1151        view["raw"]["stopOrders"] = self.RequestStopOrders()  # current actual stop orders (list)
1152
1153        # save response headers without "positions" section:
1154        for key in portfolioResponse.keys():
1155            if key != "positions":
1156                view["raw"]["headers"][key] = portfolioResponse[key]
1157
1158            else:
1159                continue
1160
1161        # Re-sorting and separating given raw instruments and currencies by type: https://tinkoff.github.io/investAPI/operations/#operation
1162        # Type of instrument must be only one of supported types in TKS_INSTRUMENTS
1163        for item in portfolioResponse["positions"]:
1164            if item["instrumentType"] == "currency":
1165                self.figi = item["figi"]
1166                curr = self.SearchByFIGI(requestPrice=False)
1167
1168                # current price of currency in RUB:
1169                view["raw"]["currenciesCurrentPrices"][curr["nominal"]["currency"]] = {
1170                    "name": curr["name"],
1171                    "currentPrice": NanoToFloat(
1172                        item["currentPrice"]["units"],
1173                        item["currentPrice"]["nano"]
1174                    ),
1175                }
1176
1177                view["raw"]["Currencies"].append(item)
1178
1179            elif item["instrumentType"] == "share":
1180                view["raw"]["Shares"].append(item)
1181
1182            elif item["instrumentType"] == "bond":
1183                view["raw"]["Bonds"].append(item)
1184
1185            elif item["instrumentType"] == "etf":
1186                view["raw"]["Etfs"].append(item)
1187
1188            elif item["instrumentType"] == "futures":
1189                view["raw"]["Futures"].append(item)
1190
1191            else:
1192                continue
1193
1194        # how many volume of currencies (by ISO currency name) are blocked:
1195        for item in view["raw"]["positions"]["blocked"]:
1196            blocked = NanoToFloat(item["units"], item["nano"])
1197            if blocked > 0:
1198                view["stat"]["blockedCurrencies"][item["currency"]] = blocked
1199
1200        # how many volume of instruments (by FIGI) are blocked:
1201        for item in view["raw"]["positions"]["securities"]:
1202            blocked = int(item["blocked"])
1203            if blocked > 0:
1204                view["stat"]["blockedInstruments"][item["figi"]] = blocked
1205
1206        allBlocked = {**view["stat"]["blockedCurrencies"], **view["stat"]["blockedInstruments"]}
1207
1208        if "rub" in allBlocked.keys():
1209            view["stat"]["currentBlockedRUB"] = allBlocked["rub"]  # blocked rubles
1210
1211        # --- saving current total amount in RUB of all currencies (with ruble), stocks, bonds, etfs, futures and currencies:
1212        view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"] = NanoToFloat(portfolioResponse["totalAmountCurrencies"]["units"], portfolioResponse["totalAmountCurrencies"]["nano"])
1213        view["stat"]["stocksCostRUB"] = NanoToFloat(portfolioResponse["totalAmountShares"]["units"], portfolioResponse["totalAmountShares"]["nano"])
1214        view["stat"]["bondsCostRUB"] = NanoToFloat(portfolioResponse["totalAmountBonds"]["units"], portfolioResponse["totalAmountBonds"]["nano"])
1215        view["stat"]["etfsCostRUB"] = NanoToFloat(portfolioResponse["totalAmountEtf"]["units"], portfolioResponse["totalAmountEtf"]["nano"])
1216        view["stat"]["futuresCostRUB"] = NanoToFloat(portfolioResponse["totalAmountFutures"]["units"], portfolioResponse["totalAmountFutures"]["nano"])
1217        view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] = sum([
1218            view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"],
1219            view["stat"]["stocksCostRUB"],
1220            view["stat"]["bondsCostRUB"],
1221            view["stat"]["etfsCostRUB"],
1222            view["stat"]["futuresCostRUB"],
1223        ])
1224
1225        # --- calculating some portfolio statistics:
1226        byComp = {}  # distribution by companies
1227        bySect = {}  # distribution by sectors
1228        byCurr = {}  # distribution by currencies (include RUB)
1229
1230        for item in portfolioResponse["positions"]:
1231            self.figi = item["figi"]
1232            instrument = self.SearchByFIGI(requestPrice=False)  # full raw info about instrument by FIGI
1233
1234            if instrument:
1235                if item["instrumentType"] == "currency" and instrument["nominal"]["currency"] in allBlocked.keys():
1236                    blocked = allBlocked[instrument["nominal"]["currency"]]  # blocked volume of currency
1237
1238                elif item["instrumentType"] != "currency" and item["figi"] in allBlocked.keys():
1239                    blocked = allBlocked[item["figi"]]  # blocked volume of other instruments
1240
1241                else:
1242                    blocked = 0
1243
1244                volume = NanoToFloat(item["quantity"]["units"], item["quantity"]["nano"])  # available volume of instrument
1245                lots = NanoToFloat(item["quantityLots"]["units"], item["quantityLots"]["nano"])  # available volume in lots of instrument
1246                direction = "Long" if lots >= 0 else "Short"  # direction of an instrument's position: short or long
1247                curPrice = NanoToFloat(item["currentPrice"]["units"], item["currentPrice"]["nano"])  # current instrument's price
1248                average = NanoToFloat(item["averagePositionPriceFifo"]["units"], item["averagePositionPriceFifo"]["nano"])  # current average position price
1249                profit = NanoToFloat(item["expectedYield"]["units"], item["expectedYield"]["nano"])  # expected profit at current moment
1250                currency = instrument["currency"] if (item["instrumentType"] == "share" or item["instrumentType"] == "etf" or item["instrumentType"] == "future") else instrument["nominal"]["currency"]  # currency name rub, usd, eur etc.
1251                cost = (curPrice + NanoToFloat(item["currentNkd"]["units"], item["currentNkd"]["nano"])) * volume  # current cost of all volume of instrument in basic asset
1252                baseCurrencyName = item["currentPrice"]["currency"]  # name of base currency (rub)
1253                costRUB = cost if item["instrumentType"] == "currency" else cost * view["raw"]["currenciesCurrentPrices"][currency]["currentPrice"]  # cost in rubles
1254                percentCostRUB = 100 * costRUB / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.  # instrument's part in percent of full portfolio cost
1255
1256                statData = {
1257                    "figi": item["figi"],  # FIGI from REST API "GetPortfolio" method
1258                    "ticker": instrument["ticker"],  # ticker by FIGI
1259                    "currency": currency,  # currency name rub, usd, eur etc. for instrument price
1260                    "volume": volume,  # available volume of instrument
1261                    "lots": lots,  # volume in lots of instrument
1262                    "direction": direction,  # direction of an instrument's position: short or long
1263                    "blocked": blocked,  # blocked volume of currency or instrument
1264                    "currentPrice": curPrice,  # current instrument's price in basic asset
1265                    "average": average,  # current average position price
1266                    "cost": cost,  # current cost of all volume of instrument in basic asset
1267                    "baseCurrencyName": baseCurrencyName,  # name of base currency (rub)
1268                    "costRUB": costRUB,  # cost of instrument in ruble
1269                    "percentCostRUB": percentCostRUB,  # instrument's part in percent of full portfolio cost in RUB
1270                    "profit": profit,  # expected profit at current moment
1271                    "percentProfit": 100 * profit / (average * volume),  # expected percents of profit at current moment for this instrument
1272                    "sector": instrument["sector"] if "sector" in instrument.keys() and instrument["sector"] else "other",
1273                    "name": instrument["name"] if "name" in instrument.keys() else "",  # human-readable names of instruments
1274                    "isoCurrencyName": instrument["isoCurrencyName"] if "isoCurrencyName" in instrument.keys() else "",  # ISO name for currencies only
1275                }
1276
1277                if item["instrumentType"] != "currency":
1278                    # adding distribution by unique companies:
1279                    if statData["name"]:
1280                        if statData["name"] not in byComp.keys():
1281                            byComp[statData["name"]] = {"ticker": statData["ticker"], "cost": costRUB, "percent": percentCostRUB}
1282
1283                        else:
1284                            byComp[statData["name"]]["cost"] += costRUB
1285                            byComp[statData["name"]]["percent"] += percentCostRUB
1286
1287                    # adding distribution by unique sectors:
1288                    if statData["sector"] not in bySect.keys():
1289                        bySect[statData["sector"]] = {"cost": costRUB, "percent": percentCostRUB}
1290
1291                    else:
1292                        bySect[statData["sector"]]["cost"] += costRUB
1293                        bySect[statData["sector"]]["percent"] += percentCostRUB
1294
1295                # adding distribution by unique currencies:
1296                if currency not in byCurr.keys():
1297                    byCurr[currency] = {
1298                        "name": view["raw"]["currenciesCurrentPrices"][currency]["name"],
1299                        "cost": costRUB,
1300                        "percent": percentCostRUB
1301                    }
1302
1303                else:
1304                    byCurr[currency]["cost"] += costRUB
1305                    byCurr[currency]["percent"] += percentCostRUB
1306
1307                # saving statistics for every instruments:
1308                if item["instrumentType"] == "currency":
1309                    view["stat"]["Currencies"].append(statData)
1310
1311                elif item["instrumentType"] == "share":
1312                    view["stat"]["Shares"].append(statData)
1313
1314                elif item["instrumentType"] == "bond":
1315                    view["stat"]["Bonds"].append(statData)
1316
1317                elif item["instrumentType"] == "etf":
1318                    view["stat"]["Etfs"].append(statData)
1319
1320                elif item["instrumentType"] == "Futures":
1321                    view["stat"]["Futures"].append(statData)
1322
1323                else:
1324                    continue
1325
1326        # total changes:
1327        view["stat"]["availableRUB"] = view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"] - sum([item["cost"] for item in view["stat"]["Currencies"]])  # available RUB without other currencies
1328        view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"] = NanoToFloat(view["raw"]["headers"]["expectedYield"]["units"], view["raw"]["headers"]["expectedYield"]["nano"]) if "expectedYield" in view["raw"]["headers"].keys() else 0.
1329        startCost = view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] / (1 + view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"] / 100)
1330        view["stat"]["totalChangesRUB"] = view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] - startCost
1331
1332        # --- pending orders sector data:
1333        for item in view["raw"]["orders"]:
1334            self.figi = item["figi"]
1335            instrument = self.SearchByFIGI(requestPrice=True)  # full raw info about instrument by FIGI
1336
1337            if instrument:
1338                action = TKS_ORDER_DIRECTIONS[item["direction"]]
1339                orderType = TKS_ORDER_TYPES[item["orderType"]]
1340                orderState = TKS_ORDER_STATES[item["executionReportStatus"]]
1341                orderDate = item["orderDate"].replace("T", " ").replace("Z", "").split(".")[0]  # date in UTC format, e.g. "2022-12-31T23:59:59.123456Z"
1342
1343                # current instrument's price (last sellers order if buy, and last buyers order if sell):
1344                if item["direction"] == "ORDER_DIRECTION_BUY":
1345                    lastPrice = instrument["currentPrice"]["sell"][0]["price"] if instrument["currentPrice"]["sell"] else "N/A"
1346
1347                else:
1348                    lastPrice = instrument["currentPrice"]["buy"][0]["price"] if instrument["currentPrice"]["buy"] else "N/A"
1349
1350                # requested price for order execution:
1351                target = NanoToFloat(item["initialSecurityPrice"]["units"], item["initialSecurityPrice"]["nano"])
1352
1353                # necessary changes in percent to reach target from current price:
1354                changes = 100 * (lastPrice - target) / target if lastPrice != "N/A" and target > 0 else 0
1355
1356                view["stat"]["orders"].append({
1357                    "orderID": item["orderId"],  # orderId number parameter of current order
1358                    "figi": item["figi"],  # FIGI identification
1359                    "ticker": instrument["ticker"],  # ticker name by FIGI
1360                    "lotsRequested": item["lotsRequested"],  # requested lots value
1361                    "lotsExecuted": item["lotsExecuted"],  # how many lots are executed
1362                    "currentPrice": lastPrice,  # current instrument's price for defined action
1363                    "targetPrice": target,  # requested price for order execution in base currency
1364                    "baseCurrencyName": item["initialSecurityPrice"]["currency"],  # name of base currency
1365                    "percentChanges": changes,  # changes in percent to target from current price
1366                    "currency": item["currency"],  # instrument's currency name
1367                    "action": action,  # sell / buy / Unknown from TKS_ORDER_DIRECTIONS
1368                    "type": orderType,  # type of order from TKS_ORDER_TYPES
1369                    "status": orderState,  # order status from TKS_ORDER_STATES
1370                    "date": orderDate,  # string with order date and time from UTC format (without nano seconds part)
1371                })
1372
1373        # --- stop orders sector data:
1374        for item in view["raw"]["stopOrders"]:
1375            self.figi = item["figi"]
1376            instrument = self.SearchByFIGI(requestPrice=True)  # full raw info about instrument by FIGI
1377
1378            if instrument:
1379                action = TKS_STOP_ORDER_DIRECTIONS[item["direction"]]
1380                orderType = TKS_STOP_ORDER_TYPES[item["orderType"]]
1381                createDate = item["createDate"].replace("T", " ").replace("Z", "").split(".")[0]  # date in UTC format, e.g. "2022-12-31T23:59:59.123456Z"
1382
1383                # hack: server response can't contain "expirationTime" key if it is not "Until date" type of stop order
1384                if "expirationTime" in item.keys():
1385                    expType = TKS_STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPES["STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPE_GOOD_TILL_DATE"]
1386                    expDate = item["expirationTime"].replace("T", " ").replace("Z", "").split(".")[0]
1387
1388                else:
1389                    expType = TKS_STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPES["STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPE_GOOD_TILL_CANCEL"]
1390                    expDate = TKS_STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPES["STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED"]
1391
1392                # current instrument's price (last sellers order if buy, and last buyers order if sell):
1393                if item["direction"] == "STOP_ORDER_DIRECTION_BUY":
1394                    lastPrice = instrument["currentPrice"]["sell"][0]["price"] if instrument["currentPrice"]["sell"] else "N/A"
1395
1396                else:
1397                    lastPrice = instrument["currentPrice"]["buy"][0]["price"] if instrument["currentPrice"]["buy"] else "N/A"
1398
1399                # requested price when stop-order executed:
1400                target = NanoToFloat(item["stopPrice"]["units"], item["stopPrice"]["nano"])
1401
1402                # price for limit-order, set up when stop-order executed:
1403                limit = NanoToFloat(item["price"]["units"], item["price"]["nano"])
1404
1405                # necessary changes in percent to reach target from current price:
1406                changes = 100 * (lastPrice - target) / target if lastPrice != "N/A" and target > 0 else 0
1407
1408                view["stat"]["stopOrders"].append({
1409                    "orderID": item["stopOrderId"],  # stopOrderId number parameter of current stop-order
1410                    "figi": item["figi"],  # FIGI identification
1411                    "ticker": instrument["ticker"],  # ticker name by FIGI
1412                    "lotsRequested": item["lotsRequested"],  # requested lots value
1413                    "currentPrice": lastPrice,  # current instrument's price for defined action
1414                    "targetPrice": target,  # requested price for stop-order execution in base currency
1415                    "limitPrice": limit,  # price for limit-order, set up when stop-order executed, 0 if market order
1416                    "baseCurrencyName": item["stopPrice"]["currency"],  # name of base currency
1417                    "percentChanges": changes,  # changes in percent to target from current price
1418                    "currency": item["currency"],  # instrument's currency name
1419                    "action": action,  # sell / buy / Unknown from TKS_STOP_ORDER_DIRECTIONS
1420                    "type": orderType,  # type of order from TKS_STOP_ORDER_TYPES
1421                    "expType": expType,  # expiration type of stop-order from TKS_STOP_ORDER_EXPIRATION_TYPES
1422                    "createDate": createDate,  # string with created order date and time from UTC format (without nano seconds part)
1423                    "expDate": expDate,  # string with expiration order date and time from UTC format (without nano seconds part)
1424                })
1425
1426        # --- calculating data for analytics section:
1427        # portfolio distribution by assets:
1428        view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"] = {
1429            "Ruble": {
1430                "uniques": 1,
1431                "cost": view["stat"]["availableRUB"],
1432                "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["availableRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1433            },
1434            "Currencies": {
1435                "uniques": len(view["stat"]["Currencies"]),  # all foreign currencies without RUB
1436                "cost": view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"] - view["stat"]["availableRUB"],
1437                "percent": 100 * (view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"] - view["stat"]["availableRUB"]) / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1438            },
1439            "Shares": {
1440                "uniques": len(view["stat"]["Shares"]),
1441                "cost": view["stat"]["stocksCostRUB"],
1442                "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["stocksCostRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1443            },
1444            "Bonds": {
1445                "uniques": len(view["stat"]["Bonds"]),
1446                "cost": view["stat"]["bondsCostRUB"],
1447                "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["bondsCostRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1448            },
1449            "Etfs": {
1450                "uniques": len(view["stat"]["Etfs"]),
1451                "cost": view["stat"]["etfsCostRUB"],
1452                "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["etfsCostRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1453            },
1454            "Futures": {
1455                "uniques": len(view["stat"]["Futures"]),
1456                "cost": view["stat"]["futuresCostRUB"],
1457                "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["futuresCostRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1458            },
1459        }
1460
1461        # portfolio distribution by companies:
1462        view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"]["All money cash"] = {
1463            "ticker": "",
1464            "cost": view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"],
1465            "percent": 100 * view["stat"]["allCurrenciesCostRUB"] / view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0 else 0.,
1466        }
1467        view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"].update(byComp)
1468
1469        # portfolio distribution by sectors:
1470        view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"]["All money cash"] = {
1471            "cost": view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"]["All money cash"]["cost"],
1472            "percent": view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"]["All money cash"]["percent"],
1473        }
1474        view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"].update(bySect)
1475
1476        # portfolio distribution by currencies:
1477        view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"].update(byCurr)
1478        view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"]["rub"]["cost"] += view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"]["Ruble"]["cost"]
1479        view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"]["rub"]["percent"] += view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"]["Ruble"]["percent"]
1480
1481        # --- Prepare text statistics overview in human-readable:
1482        if showStatistics:
1483            info = [
1484                "# Client's portfolio\n\n",
1485                "* **Actual date:** [{}] (UTC)\n".format(datetime.now(tzutc()).strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")),
1486                "* **Portfolio cost:** {:.2f} RUB\n".format(view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"]),
1487                "* **Changes:** {}{:.2f} RUB ({}{:.2f}%)\n\n".format(
1488                    "+" if view["stat"]["totalChangesRUB"] > 0 else "",
1489                    view["stat"]["totalChangesRUB"],
1490                    "+" if view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"] > 0 else "",
1491                    view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"],
1492                ),
1493                "## Open positions\n\n",
1494                "| Ticker [FIGI]               | Volume (blocked)                | Lots     | Curr. price  | Avg. price   | Current volume cost | Profit (%)\n",
1495                "|-----------------------------|---------------------------------|----------|--------------|--------------|---------------------|----------------------\n",
1496                "| Ruble                       | {:>31} |          |              |              |                     |\n".format(
1497                    "{:.2f} ({:.2f}) rub".format(
1498                        view["stat"]["availableRUB"],
1499                        view["stat"]["currentBlockedRUB"],
1500                    )
1501                )
1502            ]
1503
1504            def _SplitStr(CostRUB: float = 0, typeStr: str = "", noTradeStr: str = "") -> list:
1505                return [
1506                    "|                             |                                 |          |              |              |                     |\n",
1507                    "| {:<27} |                                 |          |              |              | {:>19} |\n".format(
1508                        noTradeStr if noTradeStr else typeStr,
1509                        "" if noTradeStr else "{:.2f} RUB".format(CostRUB),
1510                    ),
1511                ]
1512
1513            def _InfoStr(data: dict, showCurrencyName: bool = False) -> str:
1514                return "| {:<27} | {:>31} | {:<8} | {:>12} | {:>12} | {:>19} | {}\n".format(
1515                    "{} [{}]".format(data["ticker"], data["figi"]),
1516                    "{:.2f} ({:.2f}) {}".format(
1517                        data["volume"],
1518                        data["blocked"],
1519                        data["currency"],
1520                    ) if showCurrencyName else "{:.0f} ({:.0f})".format(
1521                        data["volume"],
1522                        data["blocked"],
1523                    ),
1524                    "{:.4f}".format(data["lots"]) if showCurrencyName else "{:.0f}".format(data["lots"]),
1525                    "{:.2f} {}".format(data["currentPrice"], data["baseCurrencyName"]) if data["currentPrice"] > 0 else "n/a",
1526                    "{:.2f} {}".format(data["average"], data["baseCurrencyName"]) if data["average"] > 0 else "n/a",
1527                    "{:.2f} {}".format(data["cost"], data["baseCurrencyName"]),
1528                    "{}{:.2f} {} ({}{:.2f}%)".format(
1529                        "+" if data["profit"] > 0 else "",
1530                        data["profit"], data["baseCurrencyName"],
1531                        "+" if data["percentProfit"] > 0 else "",
1532                        data["percentProfit"],
1533                    ),
1534                )
1535
1536            # --- Show currencies section:
1537            if view["stat"]["Currencies"]:
1538                info.extend(_SplitStr(CostRUB=view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"]["Currencies"]["cost"], typeStr="**Currencies:**"))
1539                for item in view["stat"]["Currencies"]:
1540                    info.append(_InfoStr(item, showCurrencyName=True))
1541
1542            else:
1543                info.extend(_SplitStr(noTradeStr="**Currencies:** no trades"))
1544
1545            # --- Show stocks section:
1546            if view["stat"]["Shares"]:
1547                info.extend(_SplitStr(CostRUB=view["stat"]["stocksCostRUB"], typeStr="**Stocks:**"))
1548
1549                for item in view["stat"]["Shares"]:
1550                    info.append(_InfoStr(item))
1551
1552            else:
1553                info.extend(_SplitStr(noTradeStr="**Stocks:** no trades"))
1554
1555            # --- Show bonds section:
1556            if view["stat"]["Bonds"]:
1557                info.extend(_SplitStr(CostRUB=view["stat"]["bondsCostRUB"], typeStr="**Bonds:**"))
1558
1559                for item in view["stat"]["Bonds"]:
1560                    info.append(_InfoStr(item))
1561
1562            else:
1563                info.extend(_SplitStr(noTradeStr="**Bonds:** no trades"))
1564
1565            # --- Show etfs section:
1566            if view["stat"]["Etfs"]:
1567                info.extend(_SplitStr(CostRUB=view["stat"]["etfsCostRUB"], typeStr="**Etfs:**"))
1568
1569                for item in view["stat"]["Etfs"]:
1570                    info.append(_InfoStr(item))
1571
1572            else:
1573                info.extend(_SplitStr(noTradeStr="**Etfs:** no trades"))
1574
1575            # --- Show futures section:
1576            if view["stat"]["Futures"]:
1577                info.extend(_SplitStr(CostRUB=view["stat"]["futuresCostRUB"], typeStr="**Futures:**"))
1578
1579                for item in view["stat"]["Futures"]:
1580                    info.append(_InfoStr(item))
1581
1582            else:
1583                info.extend(_SplitStr(noTradeStr="**Futures:** no trades"))
1584
1585            # --- Show pending orders section:
1586            if view["stat"]["orders"]:
1587                info.extend([
1588                    "\n## Opened pending limit-orders: {}\n".format(len(view["stat"]["orders"])),
1589                    "\n| Ticker [FIGI]               | Order ID       | Lots (exec.) | Current price (% delta) | Target price  | Action    | Type      | Create date (UTC)\n",
1590                    "|-----------------------------|----------------|--------------|-------------------------|---------------|-----------|-----------|---------------------\n",
1591                ])
1592                for item in view["stat"]["orders"]:
1593                    info.append("| {:<27} | {:<14} | {:<12} | {:>23} | {:>13} | {:<9} | {:<9} | {}\n".format(
1594                        "{} [{}]".format(item["ticker"], item["figi"]),
1595                        item["orderID"],
1596                        "{} ({})".format(item["lotsRequested"], item["lotsExecuted"]),
1597                        "{} {} ({}{:.2f}%)".format(
1598                            "{}".format(item["currentPrice"]) if isinstance(item["currentPrice"], str) else "{:.2f}".format(float(item["currentPrice"])),
1599                            item["baseCurrencyName"],
1600                            "+" if item["percentChanges"] > 0 else "",
1601                            float(item["percentChanges"]),
1602                        ),
1603                        "{:.2f} {}".format(float(item["targetPrice"]), item["baseCurrencyName"]),
1604                        item["action"],
1605                        item["type"],
1606                        item["date"],
1607                    ))
1608
1609            else:
1610                info.append("\n## Total pending limit-orders: 0\n")
1611
1612            # --- Show stop orders section:
1613            if view["stat"]["stopOrders"]:
1614                info.extend([
1615                    "\n## Opened stop-orders: {}\n".format(len(view["stat"]["stopOrders"])),
1616                    "\n| Ticker [FIGI]               | Stop order ID                        | Lots   | Current price (% delta) | Target price  | Limit price   | Action    | Type        | Expire type  | Create date (UTC)   | Expiration (UTC)\n",
1617                    "|-----------------------------|--------------------------------------|--------|-------------------------|---------------|---------------|-----------|-------------|--------------|---------------------|---------------------\n",
1618                ])
1619                for item in view["stat"]["stopOrders"]:
1620                    info.append("| {:<27} | {:<14} | {:<6} | {:>23} | {:>13} | {:>13} | {:<9} | {:<11} | {:<12} | {:<19} | {}\n".format(
1621                        "{} [{}]".format(item["ticker"], item["figi"]),
1622                        item["orderID"],
1623                        item["lotsRequested"],
1624                        "{} {} ({}{:.2f}%)".format(
1625                            "{}".format(item["currentPrice"]) if isinstance(item["currentPrice"], str) else "{:.2f}".format(float(item["currentPrice"])),
1626                            item["baseCurrencyName"],
1627                            "+" if item["percentChanges"] > 0 else "",
1628                            float(item["percentChanges"]),
1629                        ),
1630                        "{:.2f} {}".format(float(item["targetPrice"]), item["baseCurrencyName"]),
1631                        "{:.2f} {}".format(float(item["limitPrice"]), item["baseCurrencyName"]) if item["limitPrice"] and item["limitPrice"] != item["targetPrice"] else TKS_ORDER_TYPES["ORDER_TYPE_MARKET"],
1632                        item["action"],
1633                        item["type"],
1634                        item["expType"],
1635                        item["createDate"],
1636                        item["expDate"],
1637                    ))
1638
1639            else:
1640                info.append("\n## Total stop-orders: 0\n")
1641
1642            # -- Show analytics section:
1643            if view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"] > 0:
1644                info.extend([
1645                    "\n# Analytics\n"
1646                    "\n* **Current total portfolio cost:** {:.2f} RUB\n".format(view["stat"]["portfolioCostRUB"]),
1647                    "* **Changes:** {}{:.2f} RUB ({}{:.2f}%)\n".format(
1648                        "+" if view["stat"]["totalChangesRUB"] > 0 else "",
1649                        view["stat"]["totalChangesRUB"],
1650                        "+" if view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"] > 0 else "",
1651                        view["stat"]["totalChangesPercentRUB"],
1652                    ),
1653                    "\n## Portfolio distribution by assets\n"
1654                    "\n| Type       | Uniques | Percent | Current cost\n",
1655                    "|------------|---------|---------|-----------------\n",
1656                ])
1657
1658                for key in view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"].keys():
1659                    if view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"][key]["cost"] > 0:
1660                        info.append("| {:<10} | {:<7} | {:<7} | {:.2f} rub\n".format(
1661                            key,
1662                            view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"][key]["uniques"],
1663                            "{:.2f}%".format(view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"][key]["percent"]),
1664                            view["analytics"]["distrByAssets"][key]["cost"],
1665                        ))
1666
1667                maxLenNames = 3 + max([len(company) + len(view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["ticker"]) for company in view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"].keys()])
1668                info.extend([
1669                    "\n## Portfolio distribution by companies\n"
1670                    "\n| Company{} | Percent | Current cost\n".format(" " * (maxLenNames - 7)),
1671                    "|--------{}-|---------|-----------------\n".format("-" * (maxLenNames - 7)),
1672                ])
1673
1674                for company in view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"].keys():
1675                    if view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["cost"] > 0:
1676                        nameLen = 3 + len(company) + len(view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["ticker"])
1677                        info.append("| {} | {:<7} | {:.2f} rub\n".format(
1678                            "{}{}{}".format(
1679                                "[{}] ".format(view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["ticker"]) if view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["ticker"] else "",
1680                                company,
1681                                "" if nameLen == maxLenNames else "{}".format(" " * (maxLenNames - nameLen) if view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["ticker"] else " " * (maxLenNames - nameLen + 3)),
1682                            ),
1683                            "{:.2f}%".format(view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["percent"]),
1684                            view["analytics"]["distrByCompanies"][company]["cost"],
1685                        ))
1686
1687                maxLenSectors = max([len(sector) for sector in view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"].keys()])
1688                info.extend([
1689                    "\n## Portfolio distribution by sectors\n"
1690                    "\n| Sector{} | Percent | Current cost\n".format(" " * (maxLenSectors - 6)),
1691                    "|-------{}-|---------|-----------------\n".format("-" * (maxLenSectors - 6)),
1692                ])
1693
1694                for sector in view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"].keys():
1695                    if view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"][sector]["cost"] > 0:
1696                        info.append("| {}{} | {:<7} | {:.2f} rub\n".format(
1697                            sector,
1698                            "" if len(sector) == maxLenSectors else " " * (maxLenSectors - len(sector)),
1699                            "{:.2f}%".format(view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"][sector]["percent"]),
1700                            view["analytics"]["distrBySectors"][sector]["cost"],
1701                        ))
1702
1703                maxLenMoney = 3 + max([len(currency) + len(view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][currency]["name"]) for currency in view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"].keys()])
1704                info.extend([
1705                    "\n## Portfolio distribution by currencies\n"
1706                    "\n| Instruments currencies{} | Percent | Current cost\n".format(" " * (maxLenMoney - 22)),
1707                    "|-----------------------{}-|---------|-----------------\n".format("-" * (maxLenMoney - 22)),
1708                ])
1709
1710                for curr in view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"].keys():
1711                    if view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][curr]["cost"] > 0:
1712                        nameLen = 3 + len(curr) + len(view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][curr]["name"])
1713                        info.append("| {} | {:<7} | {:.2f} rub\n".format(
1714                            "[{}] {}{}".format(
1715                                curr,
1716                                view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][curr]["name"],
1717                                "" if nameLen == maxLenMoney else " " * (maxLenMoney - nameLen),
1718                            ),
1719                            "{:.2f}%".format(view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][curr]["percent"]),
1720                            view["analytics"]["distrByCurrencies"][curr]["cost"],
1721                        ))
1722
1723            infoText = "".join(info)
1724
1725            if showStatistics:
1726                uLogger.info("Statistics of client's portfolio:\n{}".format(infoText))
1727
1728            if self.overviewFile:
1729                with open(self.overviewFile, "w", encoding="UTF-8") as fH:
1730                    fH.write(infoText)
1731
1732                uLogger.info("Client's portfolio is saved to file: [{}]".format(os.path.abspath(self.overviewFile)))
1733
1734        return view
1735
1736    def Deals(self, start: str = None, end: str = None, printDeals: bool = False) -> tuple:
1737        """
1738        Returns history operations between two given dates.
1739        If `reportFile` string is not empty then also save human-readable report.
1740        Shows some statistical data of closed positions.
1741
1742        :param start: see docstring in `GetDatesAsString()` method
1743        :param end: see docstring in `GetDatesAsString()` method
1744        :param printDeals: if `True` then also print all records to the console.
1745        :return: original list of dictionaries with history of deals records from API ("operations" key):
1746                 https://tinkoff.github.io/investAPI/swagger-ui/#/OperationsService/OperationsService_GetOperations
1747                 and dictionary with custom stats: operations in different currencies, withdrawals, incomes etc.
1748        """
1749        startDate, endDate = GetDatesAsString(start, end)  # Example: ("2000-01-01T00:00:00Z", "2022-12-31T23:59:59Z")
1750
1751        uLogger.debug("Requesting history of a client's operations. Wait, please...")
1752
1753        # REST API for request: https://tinkoff.github.io/investAPI/swagger-ui/#/OperationsService/OperationsService_GetOperations
1754        dealsURL = self.server + r"/tinkoff.public.invest.api.contract.v1.OperationsService/GetOperations"
1755        self.body = str({"accountId": self.accountId, "from": startDate, "to": endDate})
1756        ops = self.SendAPIRequest(dealsURL, reqType="POST")["operations"]  # list of dict: operations returns by broker
1757        customStat = {}  # custom statistics in additional to responseJSON
1758
1759        # --- output report in human-readable format:
1760        if printDeals or self.reportFile:
1761            splitLine1 = "|                            |                               |                              |                      |\n"  # Summary section
1762            splitLine2 = "|                     |              |              |            |           |                 |            |\n"  # Operations section
1763            nextDay = ""
1764
1765            info = ["# Client's operations\n\n* **Period:** from [{}] to [{}]\n\n## Summary (operations executed only)\n\n".format(startDate.split("T")[0], endDate.split("T")[0])]
1766
1767            if len(ops) > 0:
1768                customStat = {
1769                    "opsCount": 0,  # total operations count
1770                    "buyCount": 0,  # buy operations
1771                    "sellCount": 0,  # sell operations
1772                    "buyTotal": {"rub": 0.},  # Buy sums in different currencies
1773                    "sellTotal": {"rub": 0.},  # Sell sums in different currencies
1774                    "payIn": {"rub": 0.},  # Deposit brokerage account
1775                    "payOut": {"rub": 0.},  # Withdrawals
1776                    "divs": {"rub": 0.},  # Dividends income
1777                    "coupons": {"rub": 0.},  # Coupon's income
1778                    "brokerCom": {"rub": 0.},  # Service commissions
1779                    "serviceCom": {"rub": 0.},  # Service commissions
1780                    "marginCom": {"rub": 0.},  # Margin commissions
1781                    "allTaxes": {"rub": 0.},  # Sum of withholding taxes and corrections
1782                }
1783
1784                # --- calculating statistics depends on operations type in TKS_OPERATION_TYPES:
1785                for item in ops:
1786                    if item["state"] == "OPERATION_STATE_EXECUTED":
1787                        payment = NanoToFloat(item["payment"]["units"], item["payment"]["nano"])
1788
1789                        # count buy operations:
1790                        if "_BUY" in item["operationType"]:
1791                            customStat["buyCount"] += 1
1792
1793                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["buyTotal"].keys():
1794                                customStat["buyTotal"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1795
1796                            else:
1797                                customStat["buyTotal"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1798
1799                        # count sell operations:
1800                        elif "_SELL" in item["operationType"]:
1801                            customStat["sellCount"] += 1
1802
1803                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["sellTotal"].keys():
1804                                customStat["sellTotal"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1805
1806                            else:
1807                                customStat["sellTotal"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1808
1809                        # count incoming operations:
1810                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_INPUT"]:
1811                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["payIn"].keys():
1812                                customStat["payIn"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1813
1814                            else:
1815                                customStat["payIn"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1816
1817                        # count withdrawals operations:
1818                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_OUTPUT"]:
1819                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["payOut"].keys():
1820                                customStat["payOut"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1821
1822                            else:
1823                                customStat["payOut"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1824
1825                        # count dividends income:
1826                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_DIVIDEND", "OPERATION_TYPE_DIVIDEND_TRANSFER", "OPERATION_TYPE_DIV_EXT"]:
1827                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["divs"].keys():
1828                                customStat["divs"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1829
1830                            else:
1831                                customStat["divs"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1832
1833                        # count coupon's income:
1834                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_COUPON", "OPERATION_TYPE_BOND_REPAYMENT_FULL", "OPERATION_TYPE_BOND_REPAYMENT"]:
1835                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["coupons"].keys():
1836                                customStat["coupons"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1837
1838                            else:
1839                                customStat["coupons"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1840
1841                        # count broker commissions:
1842                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_BROKER_FEE", "OPERATION_TYPE_SUCCESS_FEE", "OPERATION_TYPE_TRACK_MFEE", "OPERATION_TYPE_TRACK_PFEE"]:
1843                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["brokerCom"].keys():
1844                                customStat["brokerCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1845
1846                            else:
1847                                customStat["brokerCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1848
1849                        # count service commissions:
1850                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_SERVICE_FEE"]:
1851                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["serviceCom"].keys():
1852                                customStat["serviceCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1853
1854                            else:
1855                                customStat["serviceCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1856
1857                        # count margin commissions:
1858                        elif item["operationType"] in ["OPERATION_TYPE_MARGIN_FEE"]:
1859                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["marginCom"].keys():
1860                                customStat["marginCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1861
1862                            else:
1863                                customStat["marginCom"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1864
1865                        # count withholding taxes:
1866                        elif "_TAX" in item["operationType"]:
1867                            if item["payment"]["currency"] in customStat["allTaxes"].keys():
1868                                customStat["allTaxes"][item["payment"]["currency"]] += payment
1869
1870                            else:
1871                                customStat["allTaxes"][item["payment"]["currency"]] = payment
1872
1873                        else:
1874                            continue
1875
1876                customStat["opsCount"] += customStat["buyCount"] + customStat["sellCount"]
1877
1878                # --- view "Actions" lines:
1879                info.extend([
1880                    "| 1                          | 2                             | 3                            | 4                    | 5\n",
1881                    "|----------------------------|-------------------------------|------------------------------|----------------------|------------------------\n",
1882                    "| **Actions:**               | Operations executed: {:<8} | Trading volumes:             |                      |\n".format(customStat["opsCount"]),
1883                    "|                            |   Buy: {:<22} | {:<28} |                      |\n".format(
1884                        "{} ({:.1f}%)".format(customStat["buyCount"], 100 * customStat["buyCount"] / customStat["opsCount"]) if customStat["opsCount"] != 0 else 0,
1885                        "  rub, buy: {:<16}".format("{:.2f}".format(customStat["buyTotal"]["rub"])) if customStat["buyTotal"]["rub"] != 0 else "  —",
1886                    ),
1887                    "|                            |   Sell: {:<21} | {:<28} |                      |\n".format(
1888                        "{} ({:.1f}%)".format(customStat["sellCount"], 100 * customStat["sellCount"] / customStat["opsCount"]) if customStat["opsCount"] != 0 else 0,
1889                        "  rub, sell: {:<13}".format("+{:.2f}".format(customStat["sellTotal"]["rub"])) if customStat["sellTotal"]["rub"] != 0 else "  —",
1890                    ),
1891                ])
1892
1893                opsKeys = sorted(list(set(list(customStat["buyTotal"].keys()) + list(customStat["sellTotal"].keys()))))
1894                for key in opsKeys:
1895                    if key == "rub":
1896                        continue
1897
1898                    info.extend([
1899                        "|                            |                               | {:<28} |                      |\n".format(
1900                            "  {}, buy: {:<16}".format(key, "{:.2f}".format(customStat["buyTotal"][key]) if key and key in customStat["buyTotal"].keys() and customStat["buyTotal"][key] != 0 else 0)
1901                        ),
1902                        "|                            |                               | {:<28} |                      |\n".format(
1903                            "  {}, sell: {:<13}".format(key, "+{:.2f}".format(customStat["sellTotal"][key]) if key and key in customStat["sellTotal"].keys() and customStat["sellTotal"][key] != 0 else 0)
1904                        ),
1905                    ])
1906
1907                info.append(splitLine1)
1908
1909                def _InfoStr(data1: dict, data2: dict, data3: dict, data4: dict, cur: str = "") -> str:
1910                    return "|                            | {:<29} | {:<28} | {:<20} | {:<22}\n".format(
1911                            "  {}: {}{:.2f}".format(cur, "+" if data1[cur] > 0 else "", data1[cur]) if cur and cur in data1.keys() and data1[cur] != 0 else "  —",
1912                            "  {}: {}{:.2f}".format(cur, "+" if data2[cur] > 0 else "", data2[cur]) if cur and cur in data2.keys() and data2[cur] != 0 else "  —",
1913                            "  {}: {}{:.2f}".format(cur, "+" if data3[cur] > 0 else "", data3[cur]) if cur and cur in data3.keys() and data3[cur] != 0 else "  —",
1914                            "  {}: {}{:.2f}".format(cur, "+" if data4[cur] > 0 else "", data4[cur]) if cur and cur in data4.keys() and data4[cur] != 0 else "  —",
1915                    )
1916
1917                # --- view "Payments" lines:
1918                info.append("| **Payments:**              | Deposit on broker account:    | Withdrawals:                 | Dividends income:    | Coupons income:\n")
1919                paymentsKeys = sorted(list(set(list(customStat["payIn"].keys()) + list(customStat["payOut"].keys()) + list(customStat["divs"].keys()) + list(customStat["coupons"].keys()))))
1920
1921                for key in paymentsKeys:
1922                    info.append(_InfoStr(customStat["payIn"], customStat["payOut"], customStat["divs"], customStat["coupons"], key))
1923
1924                info.append(splitLine1)
1925
1926                # --- view "Commissions and taxes" lines:
1927                info.append("| **Commissions and taxes:** | Broker commissions:           | Service commissions:         | Margin commissions:  | All taxes/corrections:\n")
1928                comKeys = sorted(list(set(list(customStat["brokerCom"].keys()) + list(customStat["serviceCom"].keys()) + list(customStat["marginCom"].keys()) + list(customStat["allTaxes"].keys()))))
1929
1930                for key in comKeys:
1931                    info.append(_InfoStr(customStat["brokerCom"], customStat["serviceCom"], customStat["marginCom"], customStat["allTaxes"], key))
1932
1933                info.append(splitLine1)
1934
1935                info.extend([
1936                    "\n## All operations\n\n",
1937                    "| Date and time       | FIGI         | Ticker       | Asset      | Value     | Payment         | Status     | Operation type\n",
1938                    "|---------------------|--------------|--------------|------------|-----------|-----------------|------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
1939                ])
1940
1941            else:
1942                info.append("Broker returned no operations during this period\n")
1943
1944            # --- view "Operations" section:
1945            for item in ops:
1946                self.figi = item["figi"] if item["figi"] else ""
1947                payment = NanoToFloat(item["payment"]["units"], item["payment"]["nano"])
1948                instrument = self.SearchByFIGI(requestPrice=False) if self.figi else {}
1949
1950                # group of deals during one day:
1951                if nextDay and item["date"].split("T")[0] != nextDay:
1952                    info.append(splitLine2)
1953                    nextDay = ""
1954
1955                else:
1956                    nextDay = item["date"].split("T")[0]  # saving current day for splitting
1957
1958                info.append("| {:<19} | {:<12} | {:<12} | {:<10} | {:<9} | {:>15} | {:<10} | {}\n".format(
1959                    item["date"].replace("T", " ").replace("Z", "").split(".")[0],
1960                    self.figi if self.figi else "—",
1961                    instrument["ticker"] if instrument else "—",
1962                    instrument["type"] if instrument else "—",
1963                    item["quantity"] if int(item["quantity"]) > 0 else "—",
1964                    "{}{:.2f} {}".format("+" if payment > 0 else "", payment, item["payment"]["currency"]) if payment != 0 else "—",
1965                    TKS_OPERATION_STATES[item["state"]],
1966                    TKS_OPERATION_TYPES[item["operationType"]],
1967                ))
1968
1969            infoText = "".join(info)
1970
1971            if printDeals:
1972                uLogger.info(infoText)
1973
1974            if self.reportFile:
1975                with open(self.reportFile, "w", encoding="UTF-8") as fH:
1976                    fH.write(infoText)
1977
1978                uLogger.info("History of a client's operations are saved to file: [{}]".format(os.path.abspath(self.reportFile)))
1979
1980        return ops, customStat
1981
